 = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = =   Hi Frank & All, I think Chris Moon might be afraid (fears/paranoia?) that you&#39;ll sue him, for using YOUR Frank&#39;s Box in an UNAUTHORIZED manner (by YOU the maker) of your box. At various locations, establishing businesses (of his making, now), promoting himself as the ONLY &quot;professional&quot; that knows how to use the box, and (worst yet) making False claims with the box (as he stated on his blog reposted here) to promote himself and your box that you gave him (IMHO = a big mistake) + now profiting from your invention and yet, putting YOU and all of us researchers down as getting false communications, opening up dark portals, dark entities, etc.! Frankly, I&#39;d sue his butt, as he&#39;s Highjacked the device for his own benifit (fame & fortune, kinda like selling one&#39;s soul to the Devil - for Money & Fame). Frank, You are getting nothing out of this except being Associated with Frank&#39;s Box, and even there, Chris is unauthorised by you, to rename it, &quot;The Telephone to the Dead&quot;, which is an inacurate discription of your box! Plus, he claims he&#39;s acting like a Medium connecting the living with their departed loved ones (what proof is there of this? I&#39;d love to hear from my Dad, but may have to wait a LONG time for that to happen)! I&#39;d contact a lawyer - for infringment rights to your device (unauthorised use), on a contingency basis (pay if you win the lawsuit, from the winnings). Plus, you could get your boxes, Sony cassette recorder, and Tarot CD back, as well as put him outta business, before he does more damage!  =Judy=    P.S. He may know you well enought to know you&#39;ll never sue him, too (and thus get away with it)!  8-(
